Maintainer: Debora Zuanny <deborazuanny@gmail.com>
Description: Produces diversity estimates and species lists with associated global distribution for any angiosperm family and genus from Plants of the World Online database, by interacting with the source code of each plant taxon page, and creates global maps of species richness.
